{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Mama Subitski was a really wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we really stayed there with intermittent frights and events that threatened to expose us, where we had to stand behind doors while the postman came.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one child would have postal viewing duty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You stare out the little tiny window of this cottage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was a tiny place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know how we all managed to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Must have been about eight, nine of us-- to say, OK, the so-and-so is coming, the mayor from the nearby town or the postman is coming.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then we had to go in the potato cellar real quick, see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we became familiar with that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we were already starting to store up rations in case the Russians came, potatoes and all these important things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember that was the first time I had been in snow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Berlin is not a particularly heavy snowfall city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It gets a little bit, and it turns to dirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, there was tons of snow there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the little lake was frozen over right by the property.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But remember, they did not even own this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were poor as dirt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were sharecroppers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And you know what that means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That means you get to keep what you need to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
